~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : bcast                                     ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : bcast <message>

   This command allows the wizzes and admin to broadcast to all rooms the
   message supplying system and important info.  Command contians a 
   notification beep sequence.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : wake
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
